window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Dragons are almost extinct: Eggs are rare, and the dragons alive are in danger all because of one man.</b></p> <p>Thad Reinhart doesn’t just want dragonriders gone because their role as adjudicators threatens his businesses. His grudge is personal - but there’s one thing he didn’t anticipate.</p> <p>S. Beaufont isn’t like any dragonrider before. She’s modern, thinks differently, and definitely doesn’t look like a dragonrider. When it comes to tackling challenges, she uses new-world thinking for old-world problems.</p> <p>But will it be enough to beat an evil bent on destroying the planet?</p>"; 
